episodes.title: Jacky Hart - How The Exclusive Brethern are controlling  and restrictive
episodes.description:
Jacky speaks out about her personal experiences of being a former member of the Exclusive Brethren, explaining how and why they were so controlling, restrictive and excluded everyone from the real world.
